{# Response template for 5-star reviews.
   Populated by response-drafter agent; requires human review before posting.
   Kept brief — over-responding to positive reviews can seem performative.
   NEVER post without human approval.
#}
{# ── Apple App Store variant ──────────────────────────────────────── #}
{% if platform == "apple" %}
{% if user_tier == "enterprise" %}
Thank you — we genuinely appreciate you sharing this. Feedback like yours helps us keep raising the bar. We're glad the product is delivering value for your team.
{% else %}
Thank you so much for the kind words! We're really happy to hear {{ review.theme_label | default('it') }} is working well for you. Your support means a lot to the whole team.
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

{# ── Google Play variant ───────────────────────────────────────────── #}
{% if platform == "google" %}
{% if user_tier == "enterprise" %}
Thank you — we're glad it's delivering value. Your feedback keeps us improving.
{% else %}
Thank you for the 5 stars! So glad you're enjoying it. 🙌
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

